Name: Scroll Without Arrow: Scroll down and manually back up
Description: Tests scrolling down and manually up without using the arrow, and verifies top content.

Name: Contact Us Page: Submit contact form
Description: Verifies that the user can access the contact form, fill it, submit it, and return to the homepage.
